import React, { useContext, useState } from 'react'; import '../../assets/css/style.scss'; import { CartContext } from '../PDP/CartContex'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const Checkout = () => { const { cartItems, getTotalPrice } = useContext(CartContext); const navigate = useNavigate(); const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ firstName: '', lastName: '', phone: '', address: '', city: '', state: '', zip: '', paymentMethod: 'credit_card' }); const handleChange = (e) => { setFormData({ ...formData, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); navigate("/Payment", { state: { billingDetails: formData } }); }; return (

Checkout

Cart Details

{cartItems?.map((item, index) => (

{item.title}

${item.totalPrice}

Quantity: {item.quantity}

Size: {item.size}

))}

Total: ${getTotalPrice()}

); }; export default Checkout;
